{"type":"text","timestamp":1775872001963,"sessionID":"ses_285caf619ffesRAlW2MSoicCcL","part":{"id":"prt_d7a383ff2001CTpGCKQolZDUia","messageID":"msg_d7a3830d1001SxLxqNU7vDrV60","sessionID":"ses_285caf619ffesRAlW2MSoicCcL","type":"text","text":"I've created a comprehensive proposal for AR-025 — MetadataService 与数据模型增强. The proposal addresses key architectural improvements including:\n\n**Key Enhancements:**\n- **Unified validation framework** with pluggable validators and chain pattern\n- **State machine management** for clear agent lifecycle transitions  \n- **Plugin system** for extensibility without modifying core models\n- **Multi-environment configuration** support (dev/test/production)\n- **Sensitive data protection** with encryption\n\n**Implementation Timeline:** 6 weeks across 5 phases from framework refactoring through testing and documentation.\n\n**Approach:** Gradual enhancement maintaining backward compatibility while improving validation, extensibility, and configuration management.","time":{"start":1775872001961,"end":1775872001961}}}
